.TH "libnvme_ctrl_is_transport_fabric" 9 "libnvme_ctrl_is_transport_fabric" "July 2026" "libnvme API manual" LINUX
.SH NAME
libnvme_ctrl_is_transport_fabric \- True for a fabrics transport
.SH SYNOPSIS
.B "bool" libnvme_ctrl_is_transport_fabric
.BI "(libnvme_ctrl_t c "  ");"
.SH ARGUMENTS
.IP "c" 12
Controller instance
.SH "DESCRIPTION"
A controller is reachable either over a local transport (pcie,
apple-nvme) or over NVMe-over-Fabrics (tcp, rdma, fc, loop).
.SH "RETURN"
true if \fIc\fP uses a fabrics transport, false if local.
